Jest głównym lekarzem homeopatą w Instytucie Badań nad Homeopatią, Medycyną Holistyczną i Stresem w Medical College w Thiruvananthapuram. Wśród oferowanych przez niego usług znajdują się: leczenie cukrzycy, porady dietetyczne, leczenie wypadania włosów, zarządzanie stylem życia, leczenie nadciśnienia tętniczego, cholesterolu, diety odchudzającej oraz leczenie chorób wątroby.

ja.title: ココナッツオイルは1キロ500円。パーム油とひまわり油、どちらを買うべきでしょうか？どちらが健康に良いのでしょうか？

N S ラジェシュ・クマール医師は、ティルヴァナンタプラム州ペッタ在住のホメオパシー医師兼栄養士で、この分野で20年の経験があります。 2003年にエルナクラムのパディヤール記念ホメオパシー医科大学でBHMS（栄養学修士）を修了し、トリヴァンドラムの医科大学で臨床栄養学の学位を取得しました。

ティルヴァナンタプラム医科大学ホメオパシー・ホリスティック医学・ストレス研究所のホメオパシー医師部門の主任医師です。医師が提供するサービスには、糖尿病管理、ダイエットカウンセリング、脱毛治療、ライフスタイル管理、血圧、コレステロール、減量ダイエットカウンセリング、肝疾患治療などがあります。

id.description:
Rumah Kami .... sebuah tempat yang telah menjadi tempat tinggal kami dan memberi kami begitu banyak perhatian dan kenyamanan. Kenangan yang tak terhitung jumlahnya telah tercipta di tempat ini dan saya harus mendokumentasikannya untuk tahun-tahun mendatang. it.description:
La nostra casa... uno spazio che ci ha ospitati e ci ha offerto tanta cura e conforto. In questo spazio sono nati innumerevoli ricordi e ho dovuto documentarli per gli anni a venire. Spero che vi piaccia passeggiare per casa nostra e anche rivivere insieme a me un bellissimo viale dei ricordi!

#AhaanaKrishna
#HomeTour
#HomeVlog

Nossa Casa... um espaço que nos abrigou e nos deu tanto carinho e conforto. Inúmeras memórias foram criadas neste espaço e eu precisava documentá-las para os próximos anos. Espero que vocês gostem de passear pela nossa casa e também de relembrar um pouco da minha história comigo!

#AhaanaKrishna

fr-FR.title: VISITE DE NOTRE MAISON | Maison et souvenirs | Ahaana Krishna

D'innombrables souvenirs ont été créés dans cet espace et je me devais de les immortaliser pour les années à venir. J'espère que vous apprécierez la visite de notre maison et que vous partagerez de beaux souvenirs avec moi !

es-US.description:

ja.title: 私たちの家のツアー | 家と思い出 | アハナ・クリシュナ
ja.description:
私たちの家…私たちを包み込み、たくさんの思いやりと安らぎを与えてくれた空間。この空間で数え切れないほどの思い出が作られ、これからの未来のために記録に残しておかなければなりませんでした。私たちの家を歩きながら、私と一緒に美しい思い出の道を歩むのを楽しんでいただけたら嬉しいです！

#AhaanaKrishna
#HomeTour
#HomeVlog

pl.title: NASZA WYCIECZKA PO DOMU | Dom i wspomnienia | Ahaana Krishna
pl.description:
Nasz Dom… przestrzeń, która dała nam dom i mnóstwo troski i komfortu. W tej przestrzeni zrodziły się niezliczone wspomnienia, które musiałam udokumentować na lata. Mam nadzieję, że spodoba Wam się spacer po naszym domu i że będziecie mogli razem ze mną odbyć piękną podróż po wspomnieniach!

#AhaanaKrishna
#HomeTour
#HomeVlog

de-DE.title: UNSERE HAUSFÜHRUNG | Zuhause & Erinnerungen | Ahaana Krishna
de-DE.description:
Unser Zuhause ... ein Ort, der uns beherbergt und uns so viel Geborgenheit und Geborgenheit gegeben hat. Unzählige Erinnerungen sind hier entstanden, und ich wollte sie für die kommenden Jahre festhalten. Ich hoffe, ihr genießt den Spaziergang durch unser Haus und mögt mit mir schöne Erinnerungen schwelgen!

#AhaanaKrishna

#HomeVlog

nl-NL.description:
Ons huis... een plek die ons onderdak heeft geboden en ons zoveel zorg en comfort heeft gegeven. Er zijn talloze herinneringen ontstaan in deze ruimte en ik moest ze vastleggen voor de komende jaren. Ik hoop dat je geniet van een wandeling door ons huis en dat je samen met mij mooie herinneringen opdoet!

#AhaanaKrishna

ko.description:
우리 집... 우리를 품어주고, 우리에게 많은 보살핌과 편안함을 준 공간. 이 공간에서 수많은 추억이 만들어졌고, 앞으로의 시간을 위해 기록해야 했습니다. 저와 함께 아름다운 추억의 길을 걸으며 우리 집을 즐겁게 걸어보시길 바랍니다!

hi.description:
हमारा घर... एक ऐसी जगह जिसने हमें घर दिया है और हमें इतना प्यार और सुकून दिया है। इस जगह में अनगिनत यादें बनी हैं और मुझे आने वाले सालों के लिए इन्हें संजोकर रखना था। मुझे उम्मीद है कि आपको हमारे घर में घूमना और मेरे साथ खूबसूरत यादों की गलियों में घूमना अच्छा लगेगा!

snippet.title: Sanju Rathod : From Hungry Nights To Hits
snippet.description:
🎬 Bharti TV Podcast mein aapka swagat hai!

Aaj ke episode mein humare saath hain Sanju Rathod, ek aise artist jo Jalgaon ke ek chhote se gaon se nikal kar apne sapno ke peeche Mumbai chale aaye. Mechanical engineering complete ki, lekin ek ladki ke chalte music ki duniya mein kadam rakha. Pehla gaana “Dimple” banaya—jise 50 million views mile. Budget kaafi kam tha, doston se udhaar liya, shooting khud manage ki, aur shuruaat ke 6 mahine phone bhi nahi tha. Rap aur singing kabhi seekha nahi—sab kuch khud se kiya.

Ghar se bhaag kar aaye, kuch logon ne sahara diya, jinke ghar mein kaam karke rehne ki jagah mili. Stage se darr lagta tha, suicidal thoughts bhi aaye, lekin manifestation aur bhagwan mein vishwas rakha. Isha ko cast kiya Shaky Shaky mein—jo ek experimental song tha. Aaj Nepal aur Dubai mein shows kar rahe hain, Korea mein naya song shoot ho raha hai. Daaru-sutta kabhi nahi chhua, English zyada nahi aati, lekin unke gaano ke bacche fan hain. Maa-baap ke liye ghar aur car li, aur naye composers ke liye kuch valuable advice bhi laaye hain.

Yeh hai ek asli, raw aur inspiring kahani—sirf @bhartitv  par!

#bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya #sanjurathod

LOVE !! LIKE !! COMMENTS !! SUBSCRIBE

Lyrics - 
Rr Kime ankh laal laal ravai tere khyal bhole,
Ade kale se charitra mai manas sa dhole .
Ghar Kunba bhi chhodya manai, chhode gharke,
Yaa.. Duniya chalak kirdar sare bhole.

Kime ankh laal laal ravai tere khyal bhole,
Ade kale se charitra mai manas sa dhole .
Ghar Kunba bhi chhodya manai, chhode gharke,
Yaa.. Duniya chalak kirdar sare bhole.
Rrr Dhokhe ki ya duniya ruvavai bahot sa,
In darda kitne ak din bhugtuuuu..
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele……….

Ho sari duniya hai papi, Nuye thali mannai saafi,
Fer dam bhi lagaya pure 1 tole kaa.
Chhati pe likhaya tera naam mannai sambhoo,
Are hath pe chhapaya trishul bhole ka.
Ho sari duniya hai papi, Nuye thali mannai saafi,
Fer dam bhi lagaya pure 1 tole kaa.
Chhati pe likhaya tera naam mannai sambhoo,
Are hath pe chhapaya trishul bhole ka.
Ho.. banke sanyasi teri gel rahna sai,
Mere sir pe ho hath baba dharde nai tuuuu…
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele……….

Ho Karmandal pe lipti ya mala rudraks ki,
Is dhal mai to tera hona chahu suuu.
Babya gelya rakh ke nai uth baith bhole,
Tere damru ki lay mai baba khona chahu suuu.
Ho tere dhorai rakh le nai mannai sambhoo jiiii,
Met de nai mere aaj sare dar tuuu……..
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele……….

Sa rrr matlabi duniya farebi ade log,
Mkha koye na kise ka isa gheda la liyaaa.
Balambiye Sumit ki bhi sun le kailasi,
Ade teri dhal pahada mai yo dera laa liyaaa.
Are maar ke nai ak dusre nai sove saaa,
Mannai to re gel naath rakh fer tuuuu.
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu, 
Teri saran mai lele, Ya tu  
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele……….

snippet.title: Every Parent Teacher Meeting 🧑🏻‍🏫 | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Welcome to Every Parent Teacher Meeting — where teachers give feedback, and parents bring the real drama! 🧑‍🏫👨‍👩‍👦💥
In this hilarious sketch, we dive into the world of the parent-teacher meeting — a day feared by students across India! From kids who bring a new “uncle” or “aunty” every time, to gunda students acting innocent in front of teachers, and parents who are more clueless than their own kids — we’ve captured every type of PTM madness!
And of course, how can we forget those savage desi parents who roast their own child harder than the teacher ever could? Whether it’s a parent teacher conference or a casual PTM, one thing's guaranteed: full-on comedy and chaos! 🤣
Relive your school memories and tag that friend whose parents came to school with a full charge!

#parentteachermeeting  #comedysketch  #PTMChaos #ParentTeacherConference #DesiSchoolComedy #relatablesketch 

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

Written by - Sharjeel Shoeb

Director - Sharjeel Shoeb
Associate Director - Hitan Dhaktode

Production Design & Art - Shashank Kalekar
Production Design Associate - Shubham Shivalkar
Production Manager - Pavan Tekale
Production Asst. - Gajanan Lokhande
Runner - Nilesh Korde
Location - Takalkar Classes, Baner

Costume - Shashank Kalekar
Makeup- Shahin Bajwa

Sound Recordist - Manoj More

snippet.title: Teri Galiyon Mein (Official Video) Javed-Mohsin | Mohammad Faiz | Sanika Bhoite | Danish Sabri
snippet.description:
Mohabbat bhi wahi. Galti bhi wahi aur tabaahi bhi.

Get ready to feel every beat of heartbreak with the official video of “Teri Galiyon Mein” – a soulful tale of love, loss, and longing.

Sung by the sensational Mohammad Faiz, composed by the hitmaker duo Javed-Mohsin, and penned by the lyrical genius Danish Sabri – this one’s going to stay with you long after it ends.

Featuring the stunning Sanika Bhoite, the video narrates a a story that will tug at your heart strings. 

#TeriGaliyonMein #MohammadFaiz

Featuring the stunning Sanika Bhoite. 

🎧  Audio Credits

➟ Music composer : Javed-Mohsin
➟ Singer : Mohammad Faiz 
➟ Sufi  vocals by - Danish sabri 
➟ Lyrics by - Danish sabri 

➟ Music team :

➟ Original soundtrack theme written and composed by : Javed-Mohsin 

➟ Music produced by : Jackie Vanjari
➟ All live guitars played by : Shomu seal 
➟ Solo  violin played by : Jitender Thakur 
➟ Live sarangi played by : Muddasar Ali khan 
➟ Indian rhythm ( Tabla & dholak ) by : Raju Sardar and team , firoz khan , sanjeev sen , Zuber hussain Warsi , Tahir Hasan
➟ Percussions and side rhythm played by : Satyajit Jamsandekar
➟ Live strings played by : Prakash verma , Sunil Verma , Jitender Jawda , Shyam jawda , Prabhat kishore , sandeep thakur , dilip Bose , Mahendra Bedi , chandan singh , raju padhiyar , dilip Bose 
➟ Live strokes played by : Tapas Roy
➟ Solo Trumpet played by : Kishore Soda 
➟ Backup qawali vocals by - Sameer khan royal , Aman khan , Harshad Munir & khalid Iqbal 
➟ Song recorded @Studio 504 by : Rahul M sharma 
➟ Javed-Mohsin’s legal advisor : Rohini Vakil 
➟ Assistant Mix engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai 
➟ Mixed & Mastered by : Eric Pillai @FSOB

🎬 Video Credits

➟ Director - Sneha Shetty Kohli 
➟ Starring - Sanika Bhoite & Mohammad Faiz
➟ DOP - Girish Kant
➟ Line producer - Karan Dedhia 
➟ 1st Ad - Amitesh Sanghani
➟ Assistant director - Celestine Dcruz
➟ Assistant Costume Stylist - Neha Khub & Dhwani
➟ Associate Dop - Akshay Sarode
➟ Choregrapher - Jayshree Kelkar

➟ DI Producer - Alpa Thakkar

➟ Faiz hair - Azruddin

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Lyrics:

Mukhda :

Raas na aaya mujhko tujhse dil lagana
Hasti hai yeh duniya mujhko kehke deweena
Yaad rakhega ek din saara yeh zamana
Aankhon mein aansu lekar mera muskurana

Hai mere paas wahi jo gaya hai tu de kar

Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil lekar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa kehkar
Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil lekar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa kehkar

Antra :
Yeh maanta hoon ishq se badhkar koi jaadu tona nahi
Jise tu khel ke tod de yeh dil hai khilona nahi

Yeh maanta hoon ishq se badhkar koi jaadu tona nahi
Jise tu khel ke tod de yeh dil hai khilona nahi

Duayein de rahe hain tujhko saare gham seh kar

Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil le kar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar
Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil le kar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar

Outro :
Dhoondhne walon ko tu bata de mera pata hai teri galiyon mein
Dard mein dooba dil hai magar jeene ka mazza hai teri galiyon mein

Main hoon woh bejaan mohabaat jiski dawa hai teri galiyon mein
Duniya hai mandir masjid mein mera khuda hai teri galiyon mein

Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar

Bewafa keh kar
Bewafa keh kar

snippet.description:
@KarthikSuryavlogs 

Kumbayah Kombucha is a probiotic tea that has been fermented with SCOBY (A colony of good bacteria & yeast). It is then flavoured with fresh fruits & herbs resulting in healthy & delicious sparkling beverage. Kumbayah Kombucha stands as a Healthy Soda alternative due to low sugar & Natural carbonation. It is full of Probiotics & Antioxidants which Helps digestion, Improves mood,skin & detoxifies the liver.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: The Revolutionaries - First Look | Nikkhil Advani |Bhuvan Bam, Rohit Saraf, Pratibha Ranta, Gurfateh
snippet.description:
Here is the first look for The Revolutionaries, new series coming in 2026.

#TheRevolutionariesOnPrime, #PrimeDay

Starring: Bhuvan Bam, Rohit Saraf, Pratibha Ranta, Gurfateh Pirzada and Jason Shah.
Directed by: Nikkhil Advani
Produced by: Monisha Advani and Madhu Bhojwani

A Emmay Entertainment Production

About:
This first-look offers a glimpse into the upcoming series adapted from Sanjeev Sanyal’s celebrated and widely acclaimed book, Revolutionaries: The Other Story Of How India Won Its Freedom. The Revolutionaries tells the powerful story of brave young Indian freedom fighters who believed that armed resistance was not just vital but indispensable to ending the British Raj. The series is a stirring tribute to their extraordinary lives, sacrifices, and their unwavering, undying love for their country. Currently on floors, The Revolutionaries is being mounted on a grand scale, with filming underway across multiple locations in India, including Mumbai, Amritsar, Varanasi, Dehradun, and more. The Revolutionaries will premiere exclusively on Prime Video in over 240 countries and territories worldwide in 2026.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

#therevolutionaries #amazonprime #primevideoindia #firstlook #bhuvanbam #rohitsaraf #pathibharanta #gurfatehpirzada

snippet.title: Ashutosh Rana; Scary Iconic Villain of Bollywood | जिन्हे देखते ही लोग गालियाँ देते थे | Compilation
snippet.description:
Ashutosh Rana; Scary Iconic Villain of Bollywood | जिन्हे देखते ही लोग गालियाँ देते थे | Compilation

Ek aisa sanki darinda, jiski cheekhein aur hansi ruh tak ko hila deti hai. 'Sangharsh' mein Ashutosh Rana ne villain ko sirf act nahi kiya, balki poori tarah se jee liya. Is video mein dekhiye Lajja Shankar Pandey ke woh darawne pal jo aaj bhi logon ki ragon mein sahran daal dete hain. ‘Sangharsh’ movie mein Ashutosh Rana ne Lajja Shankar Pandey ke roop mein ek aisa khaufnaak villain play kiya tha, jise dekhkar logon ki raaton ki neend ud gayi thi. Ek pagal dharmik fanatic jo bachchon ki bali dekar moksha paana chahta hai — uske junoon, paagalpan aur darr ko Ashutosh Rana ne itni intensity ke saath dikhaya ki unke scenes dekhte hi ronge khade ho jaate hain. Is video mein dekhiye unke sabse scary, intense aur horrifying scenes ka zabardast compilation — jo dikhata hai kyun wo Bollywood ke most terrifying villains mein se ek hain.

Directed by: Tanuja Chandra,  
Writing Credits: Mahesh Bhatt, Girish Dhamija, Thomas Harris,  
Cast: Preity G Zinta, Akshay Kumar, Ashutosh Rana, Vishwajeet Pradhan, Aman Verma, Madan Jain, Alia Bhatt, Ninad Kamat, Abhay Chopra, S.M. Zaheer, Arif Zakaria, Yash Tonk, Brij Bhushan Sahni, Saurabh Dubey, Rajesh Prasher, Krishna Bhatt, Sanjeeva Vatsa, Dinesh Chaturvedi, Shahad Chavan, Naushaad Abbas, Amardeep Jha, Master Mazhar, Jash Trivedi,  
Produced by: Mukesh Bhatt,  
Music by: Jatin Pandit, Lalit Pandit, Uttank Vora,
Second Unit Director or Assistant Director: Khalid Akhtar, Rabinder Parasher, Rajesh Prasher,  
Music Department: Remo Fernandes, Jaspinder Narula, Sonu Nigam, Shraddha Pandit, Sameer, Kumar Sanu

snippet.title: Chakna & Chai With Shatrughan Sinha & Paresh Rawal At Ramayana | Sunday Brunch Ep 113 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App: https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

Veteran stars Shatrughan Sinha & Paresh Rawal come together for a legendary brunch at Ramayan—Sinha ji’s iconic home in Mumbai. From hilarious childhood memories and timeless love stories to political journeys and behind-the-scenes tales from Bollywood, this episode is packed with nostalgia, laughter, and heart.

Watch them talk about food, fame, “Khamosh!”, and everything in between — all with the unfiltered charm only legends can bring. Grab your chai and snacks, and tune in for this unforgettable Sunday Brunch with Kamiya Jani!

#SundayBrunch #ShatrughanSinha #PareshRawal #CurlyTales #KamiyaJani #Khamosh

hi.description:
हर मंगलवार और शनिवार को नया वीडियो।

मुख्य विशेषताएं:

#voiceartist #एनीमे #हिंदी डबिंग

____________________________________________________________________________________________
के बारे में:

"द मोटरमाउथ" के नाम से प्रसिद्ध एक प्रतिष्ठित आवाज़ कलाकार, सोनल कौशल, लोकप्रिय किरदार डोरेमोन को अपनी आवाज़ देने के लिए जानी जाती हैं। अपनी ऊर्जावान और भावपूर्ण आवाज़ के ज़रिए सोनल ने हर उम्र के दर्शकों के लिए इस प्रतिष्ठित रोबोट बिल्ली को जीवंत कर दिया है। गतिशील और आकर्षक किरदारों को बखूबी निभाने की अपनी क्षमता से पहचाने जाने वाले करियर के साथ, सोनल आवाज़ अभिनय जगत में एक प्रमुख हस्ती बन गई हैं। विविध भूमिकाओं के सार को जीवंत और करिश्माई उपस्थिति के साथ निभाने की उनकी क्षमता ने एक अग्रणी आवाज़ कलाकार के रूप में उनकी प्रतिष्ठा को मज़बूत किया है, जिससे वे प्रशंसकों और आलोचकों, दोनों की पसंदीदा बन गई हैं।

द मोटर माउथ शो या टीएमएमएस में, हम मज़ेदार तत्वों से भरपूर बेहतरीन कहानियाँ ढूँढ़ने की कोशिश करते हैं। टीएमएमएस मस्ती, मनोरंजन और प्रेरणा का एक बेहतरीन मिश्रण है। हम युवा प्रतिभाओं, अभिनेताओं, उद्यमियों, प्रेरक व्यक्तित्वों, एथलीटों और सभी क्षेत्रों के लोगों को अपने मंच पर आमंत्रित करते हैं।

What’s even crazier — all these Korean, Mandarin, and Chinese dramas are available for FREE on Amazon MX Player… and in Hindi 
If you love chaos, romance, aliens, and a little bit of amnesia – this is your sign.

Click below and enter the madness : https://www.mxplayer.in/show/watch-my-girlfriend-is-an-alien/seasons/season-1-1e56c74309919d397ff7ffd2bd1da5e6

Follow us on Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/only_desi/

Written by- Nishant and Ankit

snippet.description:

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun.

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: SUPERFAST Shiv Chalisa | श्री शिव चालीसा | Sohini Mishra | Shiv Bhajan | Shiv Ji Ke Bhajan | Sawan
snippet.description:
SUPERFAST Shiv Chalisa | श्री शिव चालीसा | Sohini Mishra | Shiv Bhajan | Shiv Ji Ke Bhajan | Sawan

🔱 SUPERFAST शिव चालीसा – अब और अधिक ऊर्जा और भक्ति के साथ!
Sawan 2025 के पावन महीने में सुनिए Sohini Mishra की तेज़, प्रेरणादायक आवाज़ में
श्री शिव चालीसा, जो आपके दिन की शुरुआत को बनाएगा शक्तिशाली और ऊर्जावान।

🕉️ शिव चालीसा का पाठ जीवन में लाता है:
✨ शांति,
✨ शक्ति,
✨ और भगवान शिव की कृपा।

🎧 इस सुपरफास्ट वर्ज़न को सुनें ध्यान, आरती या दैनिक पूजा के समय – और करें महादेव का आवाहन।

🔔 हर हफ्ते नए शक्तिशाली भजन और मंत्रों के लिए Subscribe करें:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7ZivIYRB0fMSGh-THcTYbw

💬 Comment करें: “हर हर महादेव 🔱” अगर यह चालीसा आपके मन को जोश से भर दे।

Title :- Superfast Shiv Chalisa
Music & Singer :- Sohini Mishra
Video :- Mindpro Agency

शिव चालीसा (Shiv Chalisa)

जय गिरिजा पति दीन दयाला । सदा करत सन्तन प्रतिपाला ॥
भाल चन्द्रमा सोहत नीके । कानन कुण्डल नागफनी के ॥

अंग गौर शिर गंग बहाये । मुण्डमाल तन क्षार लगाए ॥
वस्त्र खाल बाघम्बर सोहे । छवि को देखि नाग मन मोहे ॥

मैना मातु की हवे दुलारी । बाम अंग सोहत छवि न्यारी ॥
कर त्रिशूल सोहत छवि भारी । करत सदा शत्रुन क्षयकारी ॥

नन्दि गणेश सोहै तहँ कैसे । सागर मध्य कमल हैं जैसे ॥
कार्तिक श्याम और गणराऊ । या छवि को कहि जात न काऊ ॥

देवन जबहीं जाय पुकारा । तब ही दुख प्रभु आप निवारा ॥
किया उपद्रव तारक भारी । देवन सब मिलि तुमहिं जुहारी ॥

तुरत षडानन आप पठायउ । लवनिमेष महँ मारि गिरायउ ॥
आप जलंधर असुर संहारा । सुयश तुम्हार विदित संसारा ॥

त्रिपुरासुर सन युद्ध मचाई । सबहिं कृपा कर लीन बचाई ॥
किया तपहिं भागीरथ भारी । पुरब प्रतिज्ञा तासु पुरारी ॥

दानिन महँ तुम सम कोउ नाहीं । सेवक स्तुति करत सदाहीं ॥
वेद नाम महिमा तव गाई। अकथ अनादि भेद नहिं पाई ॥

प्रकटी उदधि मंथन में ज्वाला । जरत सुरासुर भए विहाला ॥
कीन्ही दया तहं करी सहाई । नीलकण्ठ तब नाम कहाई ॥

पूजन रामचन्द्र जब कीन्हा । जीत के लंक विभीषण दीन्हा ॥
सहस कमल में हो रहे धारी । कीन्ह परीक्षा तबहिं पुरारी ॥

एक कमल प्रभु राखेउ जोई ।कमल नयन पूजन चहं सोई ॥
कठिन भक्ति देखी प्रभु शंकर । भए प्रसन्न दिए इच्छित वर ॥

जय जय जय अनन्त अविनाशी । करत कृपा सब के घटवासी ॥
दुष्ट सकल नित मोहि सतावै । भ्रमत रहौं मोहि चैन न आवै ॥

त्राहि त्राहि मैं नाथ पुकारो । येहि अवसर मोहि आन उबारो ॥
लै त्रिशूल शत्रुन को मारो । संकट से मोहि आन उबारो ॥

मात-पिता भ्राता सब होई । संकट में पूछत नहिं कोई ॥
स्वामी एक है आस तुम्हारी । आय हरहु मम संकट भारी ॥

धन निर्धन को देत सदा हीं । जो कोई जांचे सो फल पाहीं ॥
अस्तुति केहि विधि करैं तुम्हारी । क्षमहु नाथ अब चूक हमारी ॥

शंकर हो संकट के नाशन । मंगल कारण विघ्न विनाशन ॥
योगी यति मुनि ध्यान लगावैं । शारद नारद शीश नवावैं ॥

नमो नमो जय नमः शिवाय । सुर ब्रह्मादिक पार न पाय ॥
जो यह पाठ करे मन लाई । ता पर होत है शम्भु सहाई ॥

ॠनियां जो कोई हो अधिकारी । पाठ करे सो पावन हारी ॥
पुत्र हीन कर इच्छा जोई । निश्चय शिव प्रसाद तेहि होई ॥

पण्डित त्रयोदशी को लावे । ध्यान पूर्वक होम करावे ॥
त्रयोदशी व्रत करै हमेशा । ताके तन नहीं रहै कलेशा ॥

धूप दीप नैवेद्य चढ़ावे । शंकर सम्मुख पाठ सुनावे ॥
जन्म जन्म के पाप नसावे । अन्त धाम शिवपुर में पावे ॥

कहैं अयोध्यादास आस तुम्हारी । जानि सकल दुःख हरहु हमारी ॥

॥ दोहा ॥
नित्त नेम कर प्रातः ही, पाठ करौं चालीसा ।
तुम मेरी मनोकामना, पूर्ण करो जगदीश ॥

मगसर छठि हेमन्त ॠतु, संवत चौसठ जान ।
अस्तुति चालीसा शिवहि, पूर्ण कीन कल्याण ॥

Shiv Aarti & Bhajans

https://youtu.be/E1I_05xu-ro
https://youtu.be/Eef79MK4bSA
https://youtu.be/KjuxFnWdYpk
https://youtu.be/FkqhOr_U90E
https://youtu.be/JN_EvHnCpvY

नन्दि गणेश सोहै तहँ कैसे । सागर मध्य कमल हैं जैसे ॥
कार्तिक श्याम और गणराऊ । या छवि को कहि जात न काऊ ॥

देवन जबहीं जाय पुकारा । तब ही दुख प्रभु आप निवारा ॥
किया उपद्रव तारक भारी । देवन सब मिलि तुमहिं जुहारी ॥

तुरत षडानन आप पठायउ । लवनिमेष महँ मारि गिरायउ ॥
आप जलंधर असुर संहारा । सुयश तुम्हार विदित संसारा ॥

त्रिपुरासुर सन युद्ध मचाई । सबहिं कृपा कर लीन बचाई ॥
किया तपहिं भागीरथ भारी । पुरब प्रतिज्ञा तासु पुरारी ॥

दानिन महँ तुम सम कोउ नाहीं । सेवक स्तुति करत सदाहीं ॥
वेद नाम महिमा तव गाई। अकथ अनादि भेद नहिं पाई ॥

प्रकटी उदधि मंथन में ज्वाला । जरत सुरासुर भए विहाला ॥
कीन्ही दया तहं करी सहाई । नीलकण्ठ तब नाम कहाई ॥

पूजन रामचन्द्र जब कीन्हा । जीत के लंक विभीषण दीन्हा ॥
सहस कमल में हो रहे धारी । कीन्ह परीक्षा तबहिं पुरारी ॥

एक कमल प्रभु राखेउ जोई ।कमल नयन पूजन चहं सोई ॥
कठिन भक्ति देखी प्रभु शंकर । भए प्रसन्न दिए इच्छित वर ॥

जय जय जय अनन्त अविनाशी । करत कृपा सब के घटवासी ॥
दुष्ट सकल नित मोहि सतावै । भ्रमत रहौं मोहि चैन न आवै ॥

त्राहि त्राहि मैं नाथ पुकारो । येहि अवसर मोहि आन उबारो ॥
लै त्रिशूल शत्रुन को मारो । संकट से मोहि आन उबारो ॥

मात-पिता भ्राता सब होई । संकट में पूछत नहिं कोई ॥
स्वामी एक है आस तुम्हारी । आय हरहु मम संकट भारी ॥

धन निर्धन को देत सदा हीं । जो कोई जांचे सो फल पाहीं ॥
अस्तुति केहि विधि करैं तुम्हारी । क्षमहु नाथ अब चूक हमारी ॥

शंकर हो संकट के नाशन । मंगल कारण विघ्न विनाशन ॥
योगी यति मुनि ध्यान लगावैं । शारद नारद शीश नवावैं ॥

नमो नमो जय नमः शिवाय । सुर ब्रह्मादिक पार न पाय ॥
जो यह पाठ करे मन लाई । ता पर होत है शम्भु सहाई ॥

ॠनियां जो कोई हो अधिकारी । पाठ करे सो पावन हारी ॥
पुत्र हीन कर इच्छा जोई । निश्चय शिव प्रसाद तेहि होई ॥

पण्डित त्रयोदशी को लावे । ध्यान पूर्वक होम करावे ॥
त्रयोदशी व्रत करै हमेशा । ताके तन नहीं रहै कलेशा ॥

धूप दीप नैवेद्य चढ़ावे । शंकर सम्मुख पाठ सुनावे ॥
जन्म जन्म के पाप नसावे । अन्त धाम शिवपुर में पावे ॥

कहैं अयोध्यादास आस तुम्हारी । जानि सकल दुःख हरहु हमारी ॥

॥ दोहा ॥
नित्त नेम कर प्रातः ही, पाठ करौं चालीसा ।
तुम मेरी मनोकामना, पूर्ण करो जगदीश ॥

मगसर छठि हेमन्त ॠतु, संवत चौसठ जान ।
अस्तुति चालीसा शिवहि, पूर्ण कीन कल्याण ॥

snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 FULL GOAT ROASTED MUTTON BIRYANI Recipe Cooking in Village | Arabian Biryani
snippet.description: Today in our village, we cooked a grand Arabian-style mutton biryani using three full goats. First, we boiled the whole goats in a large vessel with spices to make the meat tender and flavorful. Then, we carefully roasted each goat on a large tawa over a direct flame of firewood, adding a smoky, rich layer of flavor. After roasting, we layered the juicy mutton with aromatic basmati rice, hand-ground masalas, and traditional spices. This massive biryani was slow-cooked to perfection and shared during a village feast. A perfect blend of smoky, spicy, and tender mutton biryani with an Arabian touch.

pt-BR.title: BIRYANI DE CARNEIRO | 3 BIRYANI DE CARNEIRO ASSADOS COM CABRA | Receita de Biryani Árabe
pt-BR.description: Hoje, em nossa aldeia, preparamos um grandioso biryani de carneiro ao estilo árabe, usando três cabras inteiras. Primeiro, cozinhamos as cabras inteiras em uma panela grande com especiarias para deixar a carne macia e saborosa. Em seguida, assamos cuidadosamente cada cabra em uma tawa grande sobre fogo direto de lenha, adicionando uma camada rica e defumada de sabor. Depois de assadas, cobrimos o suculento carneiro com arroz basmati aromático, masalas moídos à mão e especiarias tradicionais. Este enorme biryani foi cozido lentamente até a perfeição e compartilhado durante um banquete na aldeia. Uma mistura perfeita de biryani de carneiro defumado, picante e macio com um toque árabe.

hi.title: मटन बिरयानी | 3 बकरे की भुनी हुई मटन बिरयानी रेसिपी | गांव में खाना बनाना | अरेबियन बिरयानी
hi.description: आज हमारे गाँव में, हमने तीन पूरे बकरों का इस्तेमाल करके एक शानदार अरबी शैली की मटन बिरयानी पकाई। सबसे पहले, हमने पूरे बकरों को एक बड़े बर्तन में मसालों के साथ उबाला ताकि उनका मांस नर्म और स्वादिष्ट हो। फिर, हमने हर बकरे को एक बड़े तवे पर लकड़ी की सीधी आंच पर सावधानी से भूना, जिससे उसमें धुएँ जैसी, भरपूर स्वाद की परत चढ़ गई। भूनने के बाद, हमने रसीले मटन पर खुशबूदार बासमती चावल, हाथ से पिसे हुए मसाले और पारंपरिक मसालों की परतें चढ़ाईं। इस विशाल बिरयानी को धीमी आँच पर पूरी तरह पकाया गया और गाँव के एक भोज में बाँटा गया। धुएँदार, मसालेदार और कोमल मटन बिरयानी का एक बेहतरीन मिश्रण, जिसमें अरबी स्वाद भी है।

ja.title: マトンビリヤニ | 3 ヤギ丸ごとローストしたマトンビリヤニのレシピ 村で調理 | アラビアンビリヤニ
ja.description: 今日、私たちの村では、ヤギ3頭を使った豪華なアラビア風マトンビリヤニを作りました。まず、ヤギを丸ごと大きな鍋でスパイスと一緒に煮込み、肉を柔らかく風味豊かに仕上げました。次に、大きなタワ（炙り鍋）に山羊を一頭ずつ入れ、薪の直火で丁寧に焼き上げ、スモーキーで豊かな風味を加えました。焼き上がった後、ジューシーなマトンに香り高いバスマティライス、手挽きのマサラ、そして伝統的なスパイスを重ねました。このボリュームたっぷりのビリヤニは、じっくりと時間をかけて完璧に調理され、村の宴会で皆でシェアしました。スモーキーでスパイシー、そして柔らかいマトンビリヤニにアラビア風の風味が絶妙に溶け合いました。

it.title: BIRYANI DI MONTONE | 3 Ricette COMPLETE PER BIRYANI DI MONTONE ARROSTO DI CAPRA Cucinare in un vi...
it.description: Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato un grandioso biryani di montone in stile arabo usando tre capre intere. Per prima cosa, abbiamo bollito le capre intere in un grande recipiente con spezie per rendere la carne tenera e saporita. Poi, abbiamo arrostito con cura ogni capretto su una grande tawa a fuoco diretto di legna da ardere, aggiungendo uno strato affumicato e ricco di sapore. Dopo la cottura, abbiamo guarnito il succoso montone con riso basmati aromatico, masala macinati a mano e spezie tradizionali. Questo enorme biryani è stato cotto lentamente alla perfezione e condiviso durante una festa di villaggio. Un perfetto mix di biryani di montone affumicato, piccante e tenero, con un tocco arabo.

de-DE.title: Lamm-Biryani | Rezept für 3 VOLLE, vom Ziegenbock geröstete Lamm-Biryani, Kochen im Dorf | Arabis...
de-DE.description: Heute haben wir in unserem Dorf ein großartiges Hammel-Biryani nach arabischer Art mit drei ganzen Ziegen zubereitet. Zuerst kochten wir die ganzen Ziegen in einem großen Gefäß mit Gewürzen, um das Fleisch zart und aromatisch zu machen. Anschließend rösteten wir jede Ziege vorsichtig auf einer großen Tawa über direkter Holzflamme, um ihr ein rauchiges, reichhaltiges Aroma zu verleihen. Nach dem Rösten schichteten wir das saftige Hammelfleisch mit aromatischem Basmatireis, handgemahlenen Masalas und traditionellen Gewürzen. Dieses riesige Biryani wurde langsam perfekt gegart und bei einem Dorffestmahl geteilt. Eine perfekte Mischung aus rauchigem, würzigem und zartem Hammel-Biryani mit arabischer Note.

es-US.title: BIRYANI DE CORDERO | 3 BIRYANI DE CORDERO ASADO DE CABRA COMPLETO Receta de cocina de pueblo | Bi...
es-US.description: Hoy en nuestro pueblo, cocinamos un magnífico biryani de cordero al estilo árabe con tres cabras enteras. Primero, hervimos las cabras enteras en una olla grande con especias para que la carne quedara tierna y sabrosa. Después, asamos cuidadosamente cada cabra en una tawa grande sobre una llama directa de leña, añadiendo una capa de sabor ahumado y rico. Después de asar, cubrimos el jugoso cordero con arroz basmati aromático, masalas molidas a mano y especias tradicionales. Este enorme biryani se cocinó a fuego lento a la perfección y se compartió durante un festín del pueblo. Una combinación perfecta de biryani de cordero ahumado, picante y tierno con un toque árabe.

fr-FR.title: Biryani de mouton | Recette de 3 biryanis de mouton rôtis au chèvre entier | Biryani arabe
fr-FR.description: Aujourd'hui, dans notre village, nous avons cuisiné un grand biryani de mouton à l'arabe avec trois chèvres entières. Nous avons d'abord fait bouillir les chèvres entières dans un grand récipient avec des épices pour rendre la viande tendre et savoureuse. Ensuite, nous avons soigneusement rôti chaque chèvre sur un grand tawa, au-dessus d'une flamme de bois directe, ajoutant une riche saveur fumée. Après la cuisson, nous avons garni le mouton juteux de riz basmati aromatique, de masalas moulus à la main et d'épices traditionnelles. Ce biryani massif a été mijoté à la perfection et partagé lors d'un festin de village. Un mélange parfait de biryani de mouton fumé, épicé et tendre, avec une touche arabe.

id.title: Biryani Daging Kambing | 3 Resep Biryani Daging Kambing Panggang Utuh | Masakan Desa | Biryani Arab
id.description: Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak biryani daging kambing ala Arab yang megah menggunakan tiga ekor kambing utuh. Pertama, kami merebus seluruh kambing dalam wadah besar berisi bumbu agar dagingnya empuk dan beraroma. Kemudian, kami memanggang setiap kambing dengan hati-hati di atas tawa besar di atas api kayu bakar langsung, menambahkan lapisan rasa berasap yang kaya. Setelah dipanggang, kami melapisi daging kambing yang empuk dengan nasi basmati yang harum, bumbu masala giling tangan, dan rempah-rempah tradisional. Biryani besar ini dimasak perlahan hingga sempurna dan dinikmati bersama dalam pesta desa. Perpaduan sempurna biryani daging kambing berasap, pedas, dan empuk dengan sentuhan Arab.

nl-NL.title: Lamsvlees biryani | Recept voor 3 hele geroosterde geitenlamsvlees biryani | Arabische biryani
nl-NL.description: Vandaag kookten we in ons dorp een geweldige Arabische schapenbiryani met drie hele geiten. Eerst kookten we de hele geiten in een grote pan met kruiden om het vlees mals en smaakvol te maken. Vervolgens braadden we elke geit zorgvuldig op een grote tawa boven een open vuur, wat een rokerige, rijke smaak toevoegde. Na het braden legden we het sappige schapenvlees in laagjes met aromatische basmatirijst, handgemalen masala's en traditionele kruiden. Deze enorme biryani was perfect gegaard en werd gedeeld tijdens een dorpsfeest. Een perfecte mix van rokerige, pittige en malse schapenbiryani met een Arabisch tintje.

pl.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 CAŁKOWITE PIECZONE MIĘSO KOZY MUTTON BIRYANI Przepis Gotowanie w wiosce | Arab...
pl.description: Dzisiaj w naszej wiosce ugotowaliśmy wspaniałe biryani z baraniny w stylu arabskim, używając trzech całych kóz. Najpierw ugotowaliśmy całe kozy w dużym naczyniu z przyprawami, aby mięso było delikatne i aromatyczne. Następnie ostrożnie upiekliśmy każdą kozę na dużym tawa nad bezpośrednim płomieniem drewna opałowego, dodając wędzoną, bogatą warstwę smaku. Po upieczeniu ułożyliśmy soczystą baraninę z aromatycznym ryżem basmati, ręcznie mielonymi masalami i tradycyjnymi przyprawami. To ogromne biryani zostało powoli ugotowane do perfekcji i podzielone podczas wiejskiej uczty. Idealne połączenie wędzonych, pikantnych i delikatnych biryani z baraniną z arabskim akcentem.

ko.title: 양고기 비리아니 | 3가지 염소 구이 양고기 비리아니 레시피 (마을에서 요리) | 아라비아 비리아니
ko.description: 오늘 저희 마을에서는 통째로 된 염소 세 마리를 사용하여 아라비아식 양고기 비리아니를 만들었습니다. 먼저, 큰 냄비에 염소 한 마리를 통째로 넣고 양념을 넣어 부드럽고 풍미 있게 삶았습니다. 그런 다음, 큰 타와(tawa)에 염소 한 마리를 넣고 장작불에 직접 구워 훈제 향과 풍부한 풍미를 더했습니다. 구운 후, 육즙이 풍부한 양고기에 향긋한 바스마티 쌀, 손으로 갈은 마살라, 그리고 전통 향신료를 겹겹이 얹었습니다. 이 푸짐한 비리아니는 완벽하게 천천히 조리되어 마을 잔치에 함께 나눴습니다. 아라비아의 풍미가 더해진 훈제 향과 매콤함, 그리고 부드러운 양고기 비리아니의 완벽한 조화였습니다.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

श्रावण मास के पहले सोमवार पर प्रस्तुत है भगवान शिव की दिव्य आरती — "ॐ जय शिव ओंकारा"।

हर हर महादेव! ॐ नमः शिवाय।
